{"categories":["newsletter","non-profit"],"collections":"","description":"Dive into the modern, sans serif design of this nonprofit email template. Its clean white background is accentuated by splashes of red and blue, symbolizing the vital importance of water donations in Africa. The template's layout draws the eye with a wave motif, emphasizing the message that every contribution makes a significant difference. It's designed to engage with an embedded video feature, allowing you to share a deeper insight into your cause. The template captures the essence of discovery, shedding light on the urgent needs of nonprofit organizations. Perfect for newsletters, this template is an effective and visually compelling tool for fostering connections and encouraging generosity.","short_description":"Discover the modern, sans serif design of this nonprofit email template. With a clean white backdrop highlighted by red and blue, it emphasizes the significance of water donations in Africa. Engage with embedded video, shedding light on your cause. Perfect for newsletters and nonprofit organizations.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/matteo-della-chiesa.jpg","description":"I've started to use Photoshop when I was 13. From 2009 to 2014, I've been a part of 5 Art Groups, doing Illustrations and Photo-manipulations, collaborating with over 150 Artists from all the Planet. In 2014, during my final school's exams, I've got my first Freelance Job at a Milan based Agency. Thanks to that first project, I started my Career as a Freelance Independent UI & Web Designer. Today, I help brands improve their online and digital presence, building usable, unique & beautiful products, mostly collaborating with Italian & US Agencies and Startups.","short_description":"","display_name":"Matteo Della Chiesa","id":"matteo-della-chiesa"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" 